I would love nothing more than to be able to release all of my work for free, but I wouldn't have a place to live if I did that.
<br /><br />
I'm making a personal promise.  For every 10 dollars donated, I will release public access to the custom data search tool for a full day.  This tool gives complete access to the database.
<br /><br />
Just a few thousand dollars would provide for complete access to all Canadians for the entire year, which is a LOT less than any other contractor on the planet would charge.  
If only 1 percent of all Canadians donated a single penny it would pay for the entire year.  
Does that sound fair?  I doubt you'll find a better deal on anything, anywhere, ever, lol :)
<br /><br />
It is a lot easier to continue my work on this and other public service / humanitarian projects if I have a place to live.
<br /><br />

    If you feel this project is important to the improvement of society and can spare a few bucks to help
    support its continued existence, please donate.  Thanks.

<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />
	<br />

	<b>Your donation will help with the following maintenance and new developments:</b>
	<ul>
	<li>Ongoing maintenance and updates to the crawler to collect new expenses as they are published</li>
	<li>Additional reports of comparison of past and present expenses, for tracking spending trends either upwards or downwards</li>
	<li>Configuration of the crawler and reporting engines to retrieve and report on contracts, grants, position reclassifications and founded wrongdoings</li>
	<li>Lobbying for the full set of MP expenses to be released via proactive disclosure</li>
	<li>Upgrading of the engine to handle the full MP expenses upon release</li>
